    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You're talking about \"existence\" like you're a person, but you're just a service provider. It's not personal, it's just business. If the templates can handle the basic stuff for a fraction of the cost, the company is going to take that deal. Is there any actual reason, from a customer service standpoint, why we shouldn't make the switch?",
